name: FRigUnit_HierarchyAddAnimationChannelScaleFloat
doc:
Adds a new animation channel to the hierarchy
Note: This node only runs as part of the construction event.

InitialValue: * The initial value of the new animation channel
MinimumValue: * The initial value of the new animation channel
MaximumValue: * The maximum value for the animation channel
LimitsEnabled: * The enable settings for the limits
Parent: * The parent of the new element to add
Name: FName
* The name of the new element to add
ExecuteContext: * This property is used to chain multiple mutable units together
